<section class="page">
<h2 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 80px;">CONGRATULATIONS!</h2>
<p class="first" text-align:="center=" style="text-align: center;"><a href="/pages/contact" title="Contact Us" style="text-decoration: underline;">Contact us</a> to begin working together to create a custom wedding cake of your (sweet) dreams. Melanie works with every client to design an unforgettable cake. The process begins by reviewing flavors, discussing design in depth, and setting up a tasting.<br /><br />Custom cakes start at $11 / slice.</p>
<hr />
<div class="split-block wedding-cakes">
<div class="left-half"><br />
<h3><img style="float: left; margin-right: 24px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1418/7404/files/diamond-icon.png?15489800370679989261" />Flavors</h3>
<p style="margin-left: 84px;">Before your tasting, we’ll send our wedding cake menu, and you’ll choose which <a href="/pages/signature-cakes/#flavors">flavors</a> you’d like to sample. We also welcome custom flavor requests - it’s your day, after all!</p>
<br />
<h3><img style="float: left; margin-right: 24px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1418/7404/files/diamond-icon.png?15489800370679989261" />Tastings</h3>
<p style="margin-left: 84px;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">We offer tastings by appointment. Select 4 flavors to sample from our flavor list (available by arrangement) or we’ll develop a custom flavor perfect for your special day. We charge $40 for a tasting appointment which is credited to your final order should you select a Mini Melanie cake.</span></p>
<br />
<h3><img style="float: left; margin-right: 24px;" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1418/7404/files/diamond-icon.png?15489800370679989261" />Delivery</h3>
<p style="margin-left: 84px;">We deliver within the tri-state area. There is an $85 delivery fee to most venues within Brooklyn, Manhattan, and Queens. For venues outside of the city, the delivery fee is based on mileage from our kitchen.</p>
